{"tid":2290064,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[耐人尋味] 狗仔出更丨大台奀星謝可逸背歌手女友 偷食有米失婚婦疑搞出人命","createTime":"2020-11-17T17:28:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T03:49:01.000Z","uid":256585,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"83113a76ebc0da5824e4d62a908a42d3e79da156","tid":2290064,"uid":256585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T17:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KAY5DiN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKAY5DiN.png&h=e5d0ffcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大台34歲奀星謝可逸演藝成績平平，家境有米的他不介意做閒角，拍過《愛&middot;回家》、《十八年後的終極告白》等劇，最近亦有份參與《使徒行者3》。《蘋果》收到讀者黃小姐報料，踢爆他一腳踏兩船，跟大台小花謝文欣玩地下情多年，兩人防洩「蜜」，甚少在社交網貼出合照，他們同為大台訓練班畢業，惟今年初謝可逸卻背着女友偷食，暗撻失婚CEO方潔盈（Jathy），有指Jathy現正懷孕。<br />\n<br />\n讀者黃小姐爆料，指謝可逸曾多次出軌，謝文欣一直被蒙在鼓裏；今年初謝可逸重複犯錯，偷食大自己1年的失婚Jathy，最近更疑似玩出火搞大肚。讀者提供了謝可逸攬着Jathy慶祝生日的合照，有人一個月前透過FB私訊謝文欣「報寸」：「想通知返你一聲，你男朋友應該搞大咗人哋個肚。」據知Jathy曾兩度離婚，與兩任前夫分別育有一子一女，現租住山頂獨立屋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201118/GPO7HX3ZNRC4NIT3QOTJ75Q5EI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201118%2FGPO7HX3ZNRC4NIT3QOTJ75Q5EI%2F&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1YtKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=66e29fd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201118%2FGPO7HX3ZNRC4NIT3QOTJ75Q5EI%2F&h=4d7cc87d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201118/GPO7HX3ZNRC4NIT3QOTJ75Q5EI/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n麻友被偷食慘慘豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58c4d2d83e5813ca3d0cc35736bdd916f47639a","tid":2290064,"uid":256585,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T17:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tfU4TTb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtfU4TTb.png&h=44120117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSugar daddy~<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/